												"icon": "outdent",
												"name": "WYSIWYG",
												"type": "wysiwyg_basic",
												"html": "<div class=\"card-wysiwyg-body d-flex flex-column h-100 w-100 flex-fill rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-area text-dark\"><h6>Resources&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Connections</h6>\n\n<p>\n\tThrough your involvement with Pathway of Hope, you’ll be introduced to both Salvation Army and other services that are available within your community which offer:\n</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>A network of support</li>\n\t<li>A sense of community</li>\n\t<li>Holistic programs</li>\n\t<li>Spiritual guidance</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>\n\t<strong>Service Connector to:</strong>\n</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Job training</li>\n\t<li>Health services</li>\n\t<li>Childcare and education</li>\n\t<li>Housing options</li>\n\t<li>Legal services</li>\n\t<li>And much more…</li>\n</ul></div>",
